<figureCitation id="13292A67FFBAFF9FE1F721E8BA98FC54" box="[159,229,912,937]" captionStart="FIGURE 9" captionStartId="23.[151,250,1555,1577]" captionTargetBox="[237,1357,224,1498]" captionTargetId="figure@23.[187,1423,197,1528]" captionTargetPageId="23" captionText="FIGURE 9. Adults in dorsal and ventral views. Taxon names appear below each set. Bia peruana: a, male, Peru, Pasco, Chuchurras (NHMUK); b, female, Peru, Pasco, Chuchurras (FLMNH); c, male, Peru, Pasco, Pachitea (MfN); d, female, Peru, Pasco, Pachitea (NHMUK); e, male, Peru, Ucayali, Pucallpa (ZSM). Intermediate between rebeli and peruana: f, male, Peru, Ucayali, Jepelacio (NHMUK)." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/569739/files/figure.png" pageId="22" pageNumber="223">Figs 9</figureCitation>
a–e, 
<quantity id="4CEA9B07FFBAFF9FE07221E8BB3BFC54" box="[282,326,912,936]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="kg" metricValue="1.1" pageId="22" pageNumber="223" unit="g" value="11.0">11g</quantity>
